'''Revos''' was an entertainment-complex city on the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Storinal]]<ref name="TCSWE">''[[The Complete Star Wars Encyclopedia]]''</ref>. The city was filled with tall curving towers made from marble. The [[Revos Spaceport]] was located there, and it was connected to the capital city of [[Scohar]] by the [[Revos-Scohar railway]].<ref name="TCSWE" />

